message.body: I think I literally ran around this building for twenty minutes looking for a computer and when all was said and done after I find a corner to sit in, I ended up with three. My God. So annoying.
I hate not having a space for myself.
I want my boo. And my squishable worrible!
I just want to squeeeeeze you.
Baby. I feel a little delirious right now.
I'm cross eyed tired hot hungry and feel like I could just ramble nonsense.

And you know when your tired. Well actually you don't know but I told you this about me before how I repeat the same thing over and over in my head when I'm tired. I keep saying spoopty you crazay. And its making me feel crazay.
Oh sorry your probably in a meeting and I'm blowing your phone.
Love you!
Ah I love you.
I was in meetings but I like coming back to these texts.
I just wish you weren't delirious.
See. There's nothing you can even say in response to all that. Haha.
Even though I like to watch the result of your delirium
Yeah. Haha. I feel like could break out into the giggles.
I love your giggles.
I love your chortles.
That is such a funny word!
Oooh my god! Text your aunt! The 2nd, the 23rd, or the 30th.
Oh right. I even remembered earlier but then forgot
About to have a meeting. After
I'll text you again in an hour.
Text your aunt! See you later :)

Can you let me know a little in advance when you think you'll be home? I'm still hungry from dinner. And you only have chicken no sides so I'm going to make macaroni and cheese for us. I just want to know when to put it on.
She should be here in 5 minutes
Ah. Ok.
I'm walking over
Text your aunt!
I can't now.
My mom just called saying my Aunt Diane died.
I was about to text you.
Oh my god. I'm so sorry. Is she the mom of your cousin who just graduated?
Yeah
My mom called crying. She's at their house now. She said Dominique is really upset.
She's about to start college
I am so sorry. This is horrible. First Jackie now you're mom's sister. I love you. Let me know if you need anything.
Okay thanks. I love you too
Hey. You doing ok?
Yeah I'm good
Are we still going tonight?
